          <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Ośmiorniczka" width="36" height="36" class="w-9 h-9 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
          <span class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate-800">Ośmiorniczka <span class="hidden sm:inline">- Leasing Po Prostu</span></span>
